    {
      "fieldId": "1a000002-0000-4000-a000-000000000002",
      "value": "Defines the default (View-agnostic) rendering baseline, a normative heading hierarchy (`depthOffset`/`titleFieldId`), a portable `format` vocabulary with an L1/L2 precedence rule, and reserves `themeRef`/`themeVariants` plus the `ThemeReference`/`ThemeVariant` types on `DocumentView` for RFC-002. Full text: rfcs/rfc-001.md."
